Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}莉佳 佐藤院 真藤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還有各務老師 教練
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}全部被躲過去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沙希 在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這一擊懷著大家的心願！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}究極…低強勢迴旋！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fs45\pos(960,982.5)}Hyper Low yo-yo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}倉科得分 3比1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}到手啦 倉科選手第三分！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}比賽時間還剩三分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}撐過這三分鐘 明日香就贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沙希 關掉平衡器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好 第一階段 解放50%…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不 100%解放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}乾？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:08:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}艾瓦貝因 第二階段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}平衡器 全部解放
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}乾…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}來吧 沉默的時間開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}調整了反重力鞋的平衡器嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不對 是完全關閉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啟動狀態下也能關閉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}艾瓦隆…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}幾年前才剛打入這個市場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}居然開發出那種技術了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.65,0:08:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}她把本來負責保護安全的平衡器關掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這樣一來就無法在空中維持平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但只要能控制得住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}也能將反重力鞋的性能發揮到最大限度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}居然能完美控制到那麼流暢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}肯定擁有超凡的體能與感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}明日香 用音速推進拉開距離
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fs45\pos(967.5,982.5)}Sonic Boost
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}直接衝向浮標！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}別想通過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}乾得分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}乾得分 3比3
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這下我們平分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沙希 到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}接下來 綠袖子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fs45\pos(1072.5,982.5)}Greensleeves
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}展現你的美麗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這…這是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那種行動是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不管如何 快點甩開她！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:10:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這是艾瓦隆和我們一同創造的完美世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}籠罩全場的靜寂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這正是艾瓦隆帶來的祭典！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}比賽中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}時…時間到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}由於3比3平分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}在休息10分鐘後 將進入延長賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}豎起耳朵 同分下開始的延長賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就是我們FC的終曲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}反正難得 也為你們準備了謝幕的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}只能被人玩弄於鼓掌中的五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一定會寂靜到美妙不已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}明日香！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}明日香！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}明日香學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}明日香！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那雙名叫艾瓦貝因的反重力鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}在競技中也能自由調整平衡器的參數嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}再加上 能自如發揮鞋子全部潛力的乾的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啊 真藤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}擁有絕對王者名號的你 也要舉手投降了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是啊…目前是 雖然很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}倉科…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我…覺得倉科…也很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}倉科嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是啊 她的實力現在還是未知數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:12:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}總覺得還有很大的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}或許她能讓我們看到更有趣的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}幹得漂亮 還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}看來那邊倒不是很輕鬆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}她那樣子 即使短短五分鐘的延長賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}似乎也撐不下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}再多一會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我還想再跟她多飛一會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}和倉科明日香…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沙希
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}明日香…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}明日香學姐 你還有HP嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}關掉平衡器 還能那樣飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}乾飛得越來越高了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這場比賽好有趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}明日香？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}教練
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我也要關掉平衡器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}太亂來了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}之前試過一次 不是完全沒辦法好好飛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}而且 我們的鞋子和艾瓦隆的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}無法在空中進行調整
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}關上平衡器就無法再打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}即使如此也想這麼做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我不想就此放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我想繼續和乾一起飛翔！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請讓我試試 教練
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}即使化為灰燼也在所不辭！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那可不行 你又不是Zephyrion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}說不定還真能當上天空霸主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喂 連美{\fnHGSSoeiKakupoptai\fs60}咲{\r}{\blur4.5}學姐都…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}晶也 相信明日香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}明日香沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}知道了 那就拜託明日香了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我也拜託你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}靠你了 明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我也是 倉科
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}感受到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我們的FC 完美的靜寂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那時候也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}美麗中洋溢著的 澄澈如雪的靜寂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那只是恐懼罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}選手間互相過招 互相戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}讓參賽者與觀眾都感到快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那才是稱為Flying Circus的運動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}只是單方面壓制對手 奪取勝利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就不能用「Circus」這個詞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fs45\pos(960,982.5)}雜技
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不知道延長賽結束後 您還會說一樣的話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}決賽延長賽即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}接下來 本屆大會首次延長賽即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}延長賽共五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}如果仍舊無法分出勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}將會進行首分勝利的較量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fs45\pos(990,982.5)}Sudden Death
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你沒有逃走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我讚許你的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}乾 我這次一定會和你飛到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}明日香！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好像已經連直飛的力氣都沒有了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:58.32,Insert-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(100,200)}空を翔けた　重なるシルエット
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:04.86,Insert-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(100,200)}背中に縋る羽を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:31.30,Insert-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(100,200)}ずっと考えてても
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:35.02,Insert-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(100,200)}多分このままじゃ駄目だよね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:43.32,Insert-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(100,200)}もっと向い風なら
